capital investment counsel inc/nc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Management
Capital Investment Counsel, Inc. of North Carolina provides investment management services. The Company offers annuities, bank investment, community foundation, corporate bonds, corporate finance, estate planning, insurance, government securities, and money management services. Capital Investment Counsel serves investors in the State of North Carolina.




Corporate Information
